channel.title: Forum Member of the Week - 09: BobTheGUYYYYY
channel.description:
<big> Featured Auxy Artist #09: @BobTheGUYYYYY </big>
![5439e5910a4b22c74bff021e11a6a8d465b0b95f_1_499x500|499x500](upload://5sflQZOQclc8HSyXl35KzUjQ12I.png)
<big>BobTheGuyyyyy </big> is a forum regular from America. A top contender in the [rapping thread](https://disco.auxy.co/t/forum-game-the-rapping-thread/6590), he plays drums and describes himself as: "a mediocre auxy user, but I have fun with the app." His love of Video games influences his music, with arcade themes featured in his tracks. He's also a guy with five Y's in his name.
> "My beats are fire, my beats are bright > My beats be burnin’ at 700° Fahrenheit > Yet every word from your mouth is so lame, > I almost forget this is a [Forum game]. > Of any game, it’s like a game of thrones > I’m sitting on platinum and you’re sitting on bones > So step it up or get out the way, > Cuz I’ve taken my roots and I’m here to stay." > > - BobTheGuyyyyy
**Week starting: 26 Feb, 2018.** - Please listen to at least one of their tracks (or more) - Provide at least one Soundcloud comment / feedback about their music during their week. - Comment in this thread once you've provided any feedback. - If you want people to comment on your week, remember to comment for others!
Check out their tracks here: https://soundcloud.com/bobtheguyyyyy/tracks
If you want to be in the weekly draw [add your name.](https://disco.auxy.co/t/forum-member-of-the-week-who-wants-to-be-involved/5518)
